Author: smk762 -  dracocanis ominator#7640
Content: LABS acts like KMD to notarise the testchains, which may or may not be fungible with each other.

Author: smk762 -  dracocanis ominator#7640
Content: test chains are not fungible with LABS

Author: smk762 -  dracocanis ominator#7640
Content: migration/fungibility requires a dPoW layer for the burn/create, which is what LABS chain manages

Author: smk762 -  dracocanis ominator#7640
Content: all LABS notaries (should) run all active test chains
